Terumo Corp. (4543)  plans to build another
factory in the  Philippines  to manufacture syringes and will
double or triple its workers in the Southeast Asian nation,
Sonny Coloma, a spokesman of Philippine President  Benigno Aquino 
said today in  Tokyo  and broadcasted on government radio.  To contact the reporter on this story:
